<div class="page_body">
<div class="log">
Taking&nbsp;into&nbsp;account&nbsp;the&nbsp;code<br/>
<br/>
fb(2,&nbsp;ar_coeff_lag);<br/>
num_pos_luma&nbsp;=&nbsp;2&nbsp;*&nbsp;current-&gt;ar_coeff_lag&nbsp;*&nbsp;(current-&gt;ar_coeff_lag&nbsp;+&nbsp;1);<br/>
if&nbsp;(current-&gt;num_y_points)<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;num_pos_chroma&nbsp;=&nbsp;num_pos_luma&nbsp;+&nbsp;1;<br/>
else<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;num_pos_chroma&nbsp;=&nbsp;num_pos_luma;<br/>
<br/>
Max&nbsp;value&nbsp;for&nbsp;ar_coeff_lag&nbsp;is&nbsp;3&nbsp;(two&nbsp;bits),&nbsp;for&nbsp;num_pos_luma&nbsp;24,&nbsp;and&nbsp;for<br/>
num_pos_chroma&nbsp;25.<br/>
<br/>
Both&nbsp;ar_coeffs_cb_plus_128&nbsp;and&nbsp;ar_coeffs_cr_plus_128&nbsp;may&nbsp;have&nbsp;up&nbsp;to<br/>
num_pos_chroma&nbsp;values.<br/>
<br/>
<span class="signoff">Reviewed-by: Ronald S. Bultje &lt;rsbultje@gmail.com&gt;</span><br/>
<span class="signoff">Signed-off-by: James Almer &lt;jamrial@gmail.com&gt;</span><br/>
</div>
